  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/7a0b9643fb3577120b9b4c76c7272b46.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lose yourself</strong> in the relaxing solarpunk breeze of Re:Fresh, a 3D exploration-platformer collectathon game where you collect materials to help repair your town after a torrential storm! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: 1.5 hours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/61b34d9188a0e42925c6a856f1e341d0.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore </strong>at your own pace in the open-ended environment and collect solar cells to upgrade your movement options. Solar cells are your main source of energy for jumping and dashing, so make sure to check every nook and cranny to find them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/f28daa4d9978b18a52d7f82fe28f662c.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Socialize</strong> with the local townsfolk and get to know your community! There's a loveable yet goofy cast of characters to find, each with unique dialogue and tidbits of information that they love to share.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/7a0b9643fb3577120b9b4c76c7272b46.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/ab88a1cb14d924bc646c316605dbc055.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lose yourself</strong> in the relaxing solarpunk breeze of Re:Fresh, a 3D exploration-platformer collectathon game where you collect materials to help repair your town after a torrential storm! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: 1.5 hours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/61b34d9188a0e42925c6a856f1e341d0.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/034dd5ecdf3dd61ec4761e7f6030e3d8.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore </strong>at your own pace in the open-ended environment and collect solar cells to upgrade your movement options. Solar cells are your main source of energy for jumping and dashing, so make sure to check every nook and cranny to find them all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/f28daa4d9978b18a52d7f82fe28f662c.avif?t=1750117714\" width=700 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.webm?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/390a7eca959f23506a2a104788c2d4f2.mp4?t=1750117714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Socialize</strong> with the local townsfolk and get to know your community! There's a loveable yet goofy cast of characters to find, each with unique dialogue and tidbits of information that they love to share.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/354d85c7c6033906925cf91e1ac473b2.poster.avif?t=1750117714\" width=600 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297650/extras/3